name: OCEAN EYES
description:
Ocean eyes was written to bring awareness about the water and oceans being contaminated and polluted with disease and toxins. Ocean eyes was a song written by Enzy to bring awareness in the collective conscience to heal our water one drop at a time.

Water is an entity and a life force full of memories. 10 % of this NFT will go towards onedrop.org
